吗？不然怕沟通不来。。。。", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "唐小维", "author_id": "d3f9a82e89a163056f13bce62e95b94e", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "pan-xiao-mie", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "99151433", "reply_comment_id": "99114694", "reply_root_comment_id": "99114694", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "很多人都问过我语言的问题，因为楼主的英语还过得去而且斯里兰卡大部分人会英语所以还OK。但我觉得，如果你真的想去看看这个世界，语言完全不是障碍！跟我一起去斯里兰卡的妞英文就很烂，但她去过的地方比我还多。还有我之前去越南发现那边很多当地人不会英语，但你不知道还有一个东西叫肢体语言吗？最后一个故事，我在泰国遇到一对年龄50以上的夫妇，他们一路从越南走到泰国，只靠3个单词：eat、drink、sleep。", "like_count": 9, "author_name": "潘绵绵", "author_id": "1c80b6d5c04aef777db7593096ef79aa", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "tu-tu-ai-xue-xi-60", "headline": "外贸人", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "609646094", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "609646094", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "推荐斯里兰卡，对女性极度不友善的地方，良心不会痛吗？", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "兔兔爱学习", "author_id": "996e602b3bc50ef153cff884a4b3fbf8", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "faynetseng", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "286886010", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "286886010", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我也喜欢kandy和亭可马里😍在路上还遇过孔雀", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "fayne cheryl", "author_id": "25158c91f706e395bdfdb477f3d83cce", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "gong-bao-ji-ding-12", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "126363167", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "126363167", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "在兰卡呆了19天 美好的回忆", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "宫爆鸡丁", "author_id": "2bbd528c428f84dd0e9c1654e9781741", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}]